{"title_page": "Plan Panni Pannanum", "text_new": "{{mi|{{Citation style|date=March 2020}}\n{{no footnotes|date=March 2020}}{{Notability|Films|date=April 2020}}\n}}\n'''''Plan Panni Pannanum''''' is an upcoming Indian Tamil-language Comedy film directed by [[Badri Venkatesh]], produced by Rajesh Kumar and Sinthan L from Positive Print Studios. The story is written by G.Radhakrishnan, dialogues by A.C Karnamurthy. The film stars [[Rio Raj]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://tamil.indianexpress.com/lifestyle/rio-raj-plan-panni-pannanum-172846/|title=5 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95; \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bb9\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95 \u2013 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1!!|date=2020-02-28|website=Indian Express Tamil|language=ta-IN|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref> and [[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambessan]] playing the lead roles. The music for the film is composed by [[Yuvan Shankar Raja]] while Cinematography is handled by Rajasekar and editing is done by Sam RDX. The first look motion poster of the film was released by [[Sivakarthikeyan]] and [[Vijay Sethupathi]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.behindwoods.com/tamil-movies-cinema-news-16/vijay-sethupathi-and-sivakarthikeyan-releases-rio-raj-remya-nambeesan-yuvan-s-plan-panni-pannanum-first-look-motion-poster.html|title=Vijay Sethupathi and Sivakarthikeyan releases Rio Raj Remya Nambeesan Yuvan\u2019s Plan Panni Pannanum first look motion poster|date=2020-01-17|website=Behindwoods|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref> \n[[File:Plan Panni Pannanum Poster.jpeg|thumb|Plan Panni Pannanum poster\n{| class=\"sortable mw-collapsible\"\n|+\n!Directed by\n|[[Badri Venkatesh]]\n|-\n!Written by\n|\n\n\nG.Radhakrishnan, [[Badri Venkatesh]], A.C Karnmurthy\n|-\n!Starring\n|\n\n\n[[Rio Raj]]\n\n[[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambessan]]\n\n[[M. S. Bhaskar|M.S Bhaskar]]\n\n[[Santhana Bharathi]]\n\n[[Robo Shankar|Robo Sankar]]\n\n[[Bala Saravanan]]\n\nThangadurai\n\n[[Viji Chandrasekhar]]\n\nPoornima Ravi\n|-\n!Music by\n|[[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]\n|-\n!Cinematography\n|Rajasekar\n|-\n!Edited by\n|Sam RDX\n|-\n!Production\n\ncompanies \n|Positive Print Studios\n|-\n!Country\n|[[India]]\n|-\n!Language\n|[[Tamil language|Tamil]]\n|}\n]]\n\n== Cast ==\n* [[Rio Raj]]\n* [[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambessan]]\n* [[M. S. Bhaskar|M.S Bhaskar]]\n* [[Santhana Bharathi]]\n* [[Robo Shankar|Robo Sankar]]\n* [[Bala Saravanan]]\n* Thangadurai\n* [[Viji Chandrasekhar]]\n* Poornima Ravi\n\n== Principal Production ==\nThe principal production of the film started with a formal Pooja on 17, October 2019 with the main cast and crew being present. The film's shoot happened in [[Chennai]], [[Vagamon]], [[Idukki district|Idukki]], [[Gangtok]] and Kupup located near China border. The shoot was wrapped up<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://silverscreen.in/movies/news/raj-remya-nambeesan-starrer-rio-shoot-wrapped-up/|title=Raj-Remya Nambeesan Starrer \u2018Rio\u2019 Shoot Wrapped Up|last=January 7|first=Silverscreen India Staff On|last2=2020|date=2020-01-07|website=Silverscreen.in|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref> in three schedules with less than 45 shooting days. The film's Post production works began thereafter. <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/movies/news/its-a-wrap-for-rio-raj-ramya-nambeesan-film/articleshow/73158799.cms|title=It\u2019s a wrap for Rio Raj-Ramya Nambeesan film - Times of India|website=The Times of India|language=en|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n== Music ==\nThe music and score is composed by [[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]. The audio rights have been acquired by [[Sony Music India]]. The lyrics for the songs are written by [[Arunraja Kamaraj]] and Niranjan Bharathi. The first single track, \"Ennodu Vaa\" was released on 27th February 2020<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mathrubhumi.com/movies-music/music/plan-panni-pannanum-ennodu-va-lyrical-video-1.4564223|title=\u0d2a\u0d4d\u0d30\u0d23\u0d2f\u0d3f\u0d1a\u0d4d\u0d1a\u0d4d \u0d30\u0d2e\u0d4d\u0d2f\u0d2f\u0d41\u0d02 \u0d31\u0d3f\u0d2f\u0d4b\u0d2f\u0d41\u0d02; \u0d35\u0d40\u0d23\u0d4d\u0d1f\u0d41\u0d02 \u0d2f\u0d41\u0d35\u0d3e\u0d28\u0d4d\u200d \u0d2e\u0d3e\u0d1c\u0d3f\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15\u0d4d|website=Mathrubhumi|language=en|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>. The song, was released live on [[Sun Music|sun music]] and was uploaded on [[YouTube (channel)|Youtube]] at the same time. \n\n\"[[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambeesan]], who has previously sung in ''[[Natpuna Ennanu Theriyuma]]'' and ''[[Damaal Dumeel]]'', has picked up the mic again for her upcoming film, ''Plan Panni Pannanum.'' With music by [[Yuvan Shankar Raja]], Ramya has sung a [[folk song]] in the film.\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cinemaexpress.com/stories/news/2020/jan/27/ramya-nambeesan-sings-for-yuvan-shankar-raja-in-plan-panni-pannanum-16724.html|title=Ramya Nambeesan sings for Yuvan Shankar Raja in Plan Panni Pannanum|website=The New Indian Express|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n\nThe audio launch happened on 11th March 2020 at [[Sathyam cinemas|Sathyam Cinemas]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://tamil.filmibeat.com/news/plan-panni-pannanum-trailer-and-audio-release-068886.html|title=\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bbf \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb.. \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcb!|last=R|first=Vinoth|date=2020-03-11|website=https://tamil.filmibeat.com|language=ta|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://view7media.com/tag/plan-panni-pannanum-audio-launch/|title=Plan Panni Pannanum Audio Launch Archives|website=View7media - latest update about tamil cinema movie reviews|language=en|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref> The trailer of the film was released alongside the audio to the press, followed by an online launch. <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/movies/news/plan-panni-pannanum-trailer-is-here/articleshow/74573084.cms|title=Plan Panni Pannanum trailer is here - Times of India|website=The Times of India|language=en|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|'''No.'''\n|'''Title'''\n|'''Lyrics'''\n|'''Singer(s)'''\n|-\n|1.\n|Plan Panni\n|[[Premgi Amaren]]\n|[[Arunraja Kamaraj]]\n|-\n|2.\n|Allola Kallolam\n|[[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambessan]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|-\n|3.\n|Kanave Urave\n|[[Shreya Ghoshal]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|-\n|4.\n|Ennodu Vaa\n|[[Rajaganapathy|Raja Ganapathy]] , [[Ramya NSK]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|-\n|5.\n|Neengum Bothail\n|[[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|}\n\n== Promotion ==\nThe film's title was unveiled on 11 January 2020 which was released by [[Sivakarthikeyan]] and [[Vijay Sethupathi]]. The first look of the motion poster was released on 17 January 2020. The teaser was released on 21 February 2020 by [[Yuvan Shankar Raja]].\n\n== '''References''' ==\n{{No footnotes|date=April 2020}}\n{{Reflist}}\n* \n\n[[Category:Upcoming films]]\n[[Category:Indian films]]\n", "text_old": "{{mi|{{Citation style|date=March 2020}}\n{{no footnotes|date=March 2020}}{{Notability|Films|date=April 2020}}\n}}\n'''''Plan Panni Pannanum''''' is an upcoming Indian Tamil-language Comedy film directed by [[Badri Venkatesh]] , produced by Rajesh Kumar and Sinthan L from Positive Print Studios. The story is written by G.Radhakrishnan, dialogues by A.C Karnmurthy. The film stars [[Rio Raj]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://tamil.indianexpress.com/lifestyle/rio-raj-plan-panni-pannanum-172846/|title=5 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95; \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bb9\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95 \u2013 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1!!|date=2020-02-28|website=Indian Express Tamil|language=ta-IN|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref> and [[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambessan]] playing the lead roles. The music for the film is composed by [[Yuvan Shankar Raja]] while Cinematography is handled by Rajasekar and editing is done by Sam. The first look motion poster of the film was released by [[Sivakarthikeyan]] and [[Vijay Sethupathi]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.behindwoods.com/tamil-movies-cinema-news-16/vijay-sethupathi-and-sivakarthikeyan-releases-rio-raj-remya-nambeesan-yuvan-s-plan-panni-pannanum-first-look-motion-poster.html|title=Vijay Sethupathi and Sivakarthikeyan releases Rio Raj Remya Nambeesan Yuvan\u2019s Plan Panni Pannanum first look motion poster|date=2020-01-17|website=Behindwoods|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref> \n[[File:Plan Panni Pannanum Poster.jpeg|thumb|Plan Panni Pannanum poster\n{| class=\"sortable mw-collapsible\"\n|+\n!Directed by\n|[[Badri Venkatesh]]\n|-\n!Written by\n|G.Radhakrishnan, [[Badri Venkatesh]], A.C Karnmurthy\n|-\n!Starring\n|[[Rio Raj]]\n\n[[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambessan]]\n\n[[M. S. Bhaskar|M.S Bhaskar]]\n\n[[Santhana Bharathi]]\n\n[[Robo Shankar|Robo Sankar]]\n\n[[Bala Saravanan]]\n\nThangadurai\n\n[[Viji Chandrasekhar]]\n\nPoornima Ravi\n|-\n!Music by\n|[[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]\n|-\n!Cinematography\n|Rajasekar\n|-\n!Edited by\n|Sam CS\n|-\n!Production\n\ncompanies \n|Positive Print Studios\n|-\n!Country\n|[[India]]\n|-\n!Language\n|[[Tamil language|Tamil]]\n|}\n]]\n\n== Cast ==\n* [[Rio Raj]]\n* [[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambessan]]\n* [[M. S. Bhaskar|M.S Bhaskar]]\n* [[Santhana Bharathi]]\n* [[Robo Shankar|Robo Sankar]]\n* [[Bala Saravanan]]\n* Thangadurai\n* [[Viji Chandrasekhar]]\n* Poornima Ravi\n\n== Principal Production ==\nThe principal productio